    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "The machines here don’t stop.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "They’ve been running since dawn. And they will have been running until night.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "I see... The focus is on how long something happens.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Yes. That’s why we use time markers.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Like ‘for hours’, ‘since morning’, ‘by the end’?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Exactly. Those tell us the length of the action.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Then let’s see if I can use them.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
